801,IssuesEvent,2015-11-12 13:46:49+00:00,23242753,c-w/Gutenberg,1324225,hugovk,,,opened,strip_headers strips too much of the complete works of Shakespeare,[],[],0,"https://www.gutenberg.org/cache/epub/100/pg100.txt

