3210,IssuesEvent,2015-11-06 18:01:35+00:00,20571759,rosenbrockc/fortpy,9452936,wsmorgan,,,opened,Occassionally the subroutine being tested isn't made public for the test.,[],[],0,"When writing a test for a subroutine called get_list_at_this_size the following error popped up.
