3293,IssuesEvent,2017-12-02 07:44:05+00:00,8292338,ultrabug/py3status,13064767,Artlant,,,closed,semicolon in on_click does not work,[],[],2,"Hello! 
It's me again (the guy asking idiotic questions related to Deadbeef), although I doubt that someone remembers me. And about a miracle, today it is not connected with the player, but indirectly.

суть в том что параметр вида:
`on_click 1 = 'exec echo $OUTPUT | xclip -selection c; notify-send ""Copied to clipboard"" ""$OUTPUT""'`
does not work. But if you replace the semicolon `;` of a symbol `&&` then everything is fine
