3928,IssuesEvent,2015-12-02 12:14:15+00:00,11753762,chrisallenlane/cheat,33210,brutus,,,closed,Use XDG Statdards for cheat directory,[],[],6,"I don't like each program to create it's own dot-dir in my home. Why not use the [XDG Stadard](http://standards.freedesktop.org/basedir-spec/basedir-spec-latest.html) instead (afaik it works under windows too)?

With [PyXDG](http://pyxdg.readthedocs.org/) it's easy: https://github.com/brutus/cheat/commit/1296e0fe48d2b227a3bee2bfee7485ba7775157e

This would result in `/home/username/.local/share/cheat` as the default dir under Linux.

",{},{}
