6757,IssuesEvent,2015-02-20 11:04:11+00:00,5063914,douglasmiranda/django-admin-bootstrap,8349902,Seether85,,,opened,Collapsed fieldsets in forms,[],[],0,"Are they working any differently than in plain Django Admin?
A simple attempt like this:
```
    fieldsets = (
        (None, {
            'fields': ('cliente', 'codice', 'stato', 'data_primo_contatto', 'presenza_software')
        }),
        ('Dettagli commessa', {
            'classes': ('collapse',),
            'fields': ('data_inizio', 'data_fine', 'moduli', 'ore', 'prodotto')
        }),
    )
```
simply makes the whole block completely invisible, although present in html code:
