6767,IssuesEvent,2015-05-01 23:22:59+00:00,4980199,douglasmiranda/django-wysiwyg-redactor,542013,douglasmiranda,,,closed,Doesn't work with inlines,"[{'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/douglasmiranda/django-wysiwyg-redactor/labels/enhancement', 'name': 'enhancement', 'color': '84b6eb'}]",[],4,"I had to add this:

```
+            $(document).bind('DOMNodeInserted', function(e) {
+                $(e.target).find('.redactor_box textarea').redactor(
+                    {""lang"": ""en"", ""fileUpload"": ""/redactor/upload/file/"", 
+                    ""focus"": ""false"", ""imageUpload"": ""/redactor/upload/image/""});
+            });
```

Of course, it's hard coded, a better solution should be implemented. I think that inline <script> doesn't work well with inlines, and DOMNodeInserted should be monitored anyway.",{},{}
