9413,IssuesEvent,2015-09-04 12:00:22+00:00,2665618,inveniosoftware/invenio,119349,kaplun,1157480,inveniosoftware,closed,profile: nickname in profile form should not be mandatory ?,"[{'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/inveniosoftware/invenio/labels/p_blocker', 'name': 'p_blocker', 'color': 'e11d21'}, {'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/inveniosoftware/invenio/labels/question', 'name': 'question', 'color': 'cc317c'}, {'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/inveniosoftware/invenio/labels/RFC', 'name': 'RFC', 'color': '009800'}, {'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/inveniosoftware/invenio/labels/s_INSPIRE', 'name': 's_INSPIRE', 'color': '207de5'}]",[],15,"Currently in the user profile form https://github.com/inveniosoftware/invenio/blob/master/invenio/modules/accounts/forms.py#L183 the nickname is required.

