9422,IssuesEvent,2016-07-05 08:59:51+00:00,2665618,inveniosoftware/invenio,189798,jirikuncar,1157480,inveniosoftware,closed,BibHarvest OAI-PMH server performance improvement,"[{'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/inveniosoftware/invenio/labels/c_DocExtract', 'name': 'c_DocExtract', 'color': 'ededed'}, {'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/inveniosoftware/invenio/labels/c_OAIRepository', 'name': 'c_OAIRepository', 'color': 'ededed'}, {'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/inveniosoftware/invenio/labels/p_minor', 'name': 'p_minor', 'color': 'f7c6c7'}, {'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/inveniosoftware/invenio/labels/t_enhancement', 'name': 't_enhancement', 'color': 'eb6420'}]",[],4,"Originally by *vbanos* on 2012-08-20

Current OAI-PMH server functions (file: oai_repository_server.py):
* get_modification_date, 
* get_earliest_datestamp, 
* get_latest_datestamp
do the following actions:
* retrieve a record's datetime from mysql with an SQL SELECT,
* parse it to python datetime
* convert it to UTC and return it
All this processing is done in function localtime_to_utc.

The suggested improvement is that datetime is convert to UTC inside the SQL SELECT using mysql function CONVERT_TZ.

The result is better performance and less python code.",{},{}
9427,IssuesEvent,2017-10-03 13:24:25+00:00,2665618,inveniosoftware/invenio,1698163,lnielsen,1157480,inveniosoftware,opened,RFC Change license of Invenio v3 to MIT license,"[{'id': 414883139, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/inveniosoftware/invenio/labels/Type:%20RFC', 'name': 'Type: RFC', 'color': 'ffaa00', 'default': False}]","[{'login': 'lnielsen', 'id': 1698163, 'avatar_url': 'https://avatars3.githubusercontent.com/u/1698163?v=4', 'gravatar_id': '', 'url': 'https://api.github.com/users/lnielsen', 'html_url': 'https://github.com/lnielsen', 'followers_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/lnielsen/followers', 'following_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/lnielsen/following{/other_user}', 'gists_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/lnielsen/gists{/gist_id}', 'starred_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/lnielsen/starred{/owner}{/repo}', 'subscriptions_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/lnielsen/subscriptions', 'organizations_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/lnielsen/orgs', 'repos_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/lnielsen/repos', 'events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/lnielsen/events{/privacy}', 'received_events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/lnielsen/received_events', 'type': 'User', 'site_admin': False}]",0,"### Proposal

