11856,IssuesEvent,2017-01-06 03:25:38+00:00,22978655,googlemaps/google-maps-services-python,116385,stephenmcd,3717923,googlemaps,closed,The most outside brace '['  is superfluous?,[],[],1,"Python client:

```
gmaps.geocode('1600 Amphitheatre Parkway, Mountain View, CA')
----->[<-------{u'address_components': [{u'long_name': u'1600',
        Here  
```

Official API:

```
{
   ""results"" : [
```

Is this brace superfluous?

