```
router bgp 33047
 bgp bestpath as-path multipath-relax
 ...
 address-family ipv4
  ...
  neighbor 10.110.0.30 activate
  neighbor 10.110.0.30 send-community
  neighbor 10.110.0.30 route-reflector-client
  neighbor 10.110.0.30 soft-reconfiguration inbound
  ...
  maximum-paths 3
```

As an example route that now has 2 paths:

```
BGP routing table entry for 103.243.14.0/24, version 236324692
