pinging @kalefranz 

I finally upgraded from 4.1.11, and it broke my multiuser environment setup.

Using 4.2.9, it sees that the root environment is read only, but for whatever reason still appends it to the package cache and envs dirs.

ETA - More specifically, we saw this issue here:

https://github.com/conda/conda/issues/3469

We also ran into issues creating environments, if it saw a package in the root environment it would try to decompress it, but would obviously run into write issues.

