- LOG_FORMAT also needs to be updated
- LOG_FORMAT_MAP adds complexity that I failed to understand. It seems completely unused. Seems unused in the end, the ""extra"" parameter when logging is pointless? Got me wondering if it was an attempt to not use %s but named arguments in the format string, but gave up. I probably missed something here. I should've looked at the tests early, now I'm out of time for today :/",{},{}
