14376,IssuesEvent,2018-08-06 09:26:08+00:00,18508013,PyCQA/pyflakes,9711846,scolby33,8749848,PyCQA,opened,F821 Error with Forward Reference and ``from __future__ import annotations`,[],[],0,"With this example file:

```python
# test.py
from __future__ import annotations
from dataclasses import dataclass

@dataclass
class MyData:
    member: MyMember

@dataclass
class MyMember:
    value: int
```

I get an F821 error:
```shell
$ flake8 --select=F test.py
test.py:8:13: F821 undefined name 'MyMember'
```

