15543,IssuesEvent,2017-11-16 04:33:18+00:00,32944298,Z3Prover/z3,3085284,NikolajBjorner,11668813,Z3Prover,closed,Incorrect SAT,[],[],0,"When I run the following I get an incorrect SAT:
