<li>exit code is reliable reported for CLI validation error (<a href=""https://urls.greenkeeper.io/polomsky"" class=""user-mention"">@polomsky</a>)</li>
<li><code>stats</code> options are now validated by schema (<a href=""https://urls.greenkeeper.io/esbenp"" class=""user-mention"">@esbenp</a>)</li>
<li>fixes problem when using the <code>CommonsChunkPlugin</code> in async mode without <code>name</code> argument</li>
<li>fixes description of <code>--resolve-extensions</code> (<a href=""https://urls.greenkeeper.io/tomek-d"" class=""user-mention"">@tomek-d</a>)</li>
<li>fixes <code>has no internal name</code> when using dependency variable in root of scope-hoisted modules (<code>ModuleConcatenationPlugin</code>)</li>
</ul>
