DataFrameParseException: Cannot parse object as JSON: '['b\'{""section"":...""
```

This is string representing an array of results. Oddly enough, each element in the array starts with b\', which makes me believe something first treated the result strings as byte literals (prepended b') and then turned it back into a string, escaping the quote. Has anyone else used this successfully? I tried manually posting the code to Livy and got a well-formatted json string without the b'",{},{}
