16351,IssuesEvent,2018-03-13 17:30:49+00:00,46374199,IntelRealSense/librealsense,36970260,RobO-Intel,14095512,IntelRealSense,closed,Test,[],[],0,"* Before opening a new issue, we wanted to provide you with some useful suggestions (Click ""Preview"" above for a better view):

    * Consider checking out SDK [examples](https://github.com/IntelRealSense/librealsense/tree/master/examples#sample-code-for-intel-realsense-cameras).
