16545,IssuesEvent,2018-06-14 19:30:10+00:00,85903189,graphql-python/graphql-server-core,1318438,NiklasRosenstein,15002022,graphql-python,opened,Variables in get_response() are ignores,[],[],0,"To reproduce:

```python
