16871,IssuesEvent,2017-04-21 23:07:01+00:00,55101236,googleapis/artman,5422149,vchudnov-g,16785467,googleapis,opened,"artman seems to expect toolkit under reporoot, in spite of explicit override in config",[],[],0,"Using `configure-artman`, I set up my `toolkit` dir to point to the place where I had cloned the toolkit repo, which was not under `reporoot`. I then tried to generate the GAPIC for pubsub as per artman's `README` instructions, and it failed.

