18129,IssuesEvent,2017-01-12 18:52:42+00:00,68376693,pybel/pybel,5069736,cthoyt,22892058,pybel,closed,Switch tests to use local BEL resource files,[],"[{'login': 'cthoyt', 'id': 5069736, 'avatar_url': 'https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/5069736?v=3', 'gravatar_id': '', 'url': 'https://api.github.com/users/cthoyt', 'html_url': 'https://github.com/cthoyt', 'followers_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/cthoyt/followers', 'following_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/cthoyt/following{/other_user}', 'gists_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/cthoyt/gists{/gist_id}', 'starred_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/cthoyt/starred{/owner}{/repo}', 'subscriptions_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/cthoyt/subscriptions', 'organizations_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/cthoyt/orgs', 'repos_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/cthoyt/repos', 'events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/cthoyt/events{/privacy}', 'received_events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/cthoyt/received_events', 'type': 'User', 'site_admin': False}]",0,"Most tests are requesting tons of resources by URL. This makes things slow, so refactor to use `file://` paths (this is already implemented with the `requests_file` file adapter

- [x] Mocks for bel
- [x] Mocks for belanno 
- [x] Mocks for belns
- [x] Mocks for beleq
- [x] Mocks for `pybel.manager.utils.OwlParser`
- [x] Mocks for OntoSpy

Notes

- Monkey patch `pybel.manager.utils.requests.Session` for getting the internal file parser
- Monkey patch OntoSpy by messing with `loader.py`'s function, `resolve_redirects_if_needed` which is supposed to fix URI's before giving them to `RDFLib`, so just replace the result with a file-like backed by the right file (it goes in to `rdflib.graph.parse`'s source parameter, which either takes a string URI or file-like)",{},{}
